    "Id": "chassisdef_emperor_crab_EMP-CRB-XX",
    "Name": "Emperor Crab",
    "Details": "The EMP-CRB-XX delivers overwhelming ranged firepower from a 200-ton superheavy frame. Twin Improved Heavy Gauss Rifles in each side torso form the core punch, supported by a pair of Enhanced LRM 20s with Artemis IV guidance split across both arms. A Heavy PPC in the center torso rounds out the arsenal. CASE II protects all ammunition bays and a head-mounted Laser AMS handles incoming missiles. Twenty double heat sinks manage the considerable thermal load.\n\n<b><color=#e62e00>Quirk: Accurate Weapon - Gauss</color></b>\n\n<b><color=#e62e00>Drop Cost Multiplier: 1.44</color></b>\n\n<color=#FFEF00>Arm Actuator Limits: Left Lower, Right Lower</color>",
