  "StockRole": "Superheavy",
  "YangsThoughts": "Cosara built this thing out of pure ambition basically. Project Scuttle they called it, mid 32nd century. Two hundred tons, XXL engine, price tag that would make a Lyran noble choke. Draconis Combine bought some, Capellans too. Even Clan Sea Fox picked one up and nobody really knows why. Less than a dozen ever made, not sure if it was good or bad lucky to find one of them to spend money on restoring.",
